					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">When I first started, I greatly underestimated how sensible Shiru's neslib was.<br /><br />Nmi:<br />Oam update<br />Palette update (if needed) (from a buffer)<br />VRAM update (if needed) (from a buffer)<br />Set scroll<br />(Increase frame counter)<br />Music<br /><br />Main loop:<br />(wait for frame counter to tick up)<br />Controller read<br />Game logic<br />Clear oam buffer<br />Fill oam buffer<br />Fill vram buffer, or just change a pointer to a new array</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
